## 技术SEO
<a id="technical-seo"></a>

### 性能优化

1. **启用代码压缩**：
   - 使用mkdocs-minify-plugin压缩HTML、CSS和JavaScript

2. **优化JavaScript**：
   - 延迟加载非关键JavaScript
   - 在动画演示页面添加加载指示器

3. **响应式设计**：
   - 确保网站在移动设备上表现良好
   - 测试不同屏幕尺寸的用户体验

### 结构化数据

在`docs/assets/js/structured-data.js`中添加结构化数据：

```javascript
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
  const structuredData = {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebSite",
    "name": "算法可视化指南",
    "url": "https://jsdiff.com/",
    "description": "交互式算法可视化学习平台，提供差异算法、排序算法等多种算法的动态演示和详细解析",
    "potentialAction": {
      "@type": "SearchAction",
      "target": "https://jsdiff.com/search?q={search_term_string}",
      "query-input": "required name=search_term_string"
    }
  };

  const script = document.createElement('script');
  script.type = 'application/ld+json';
  script.text = JSON.stringify(structuredData);
  document.head.appendChild(script);
});
```

然后在`mkdocs.yml`中引用：

```yaml
extra_javascript:
  - assets/js/structured-data.js
```

## Vercel部署优化
<a id="vercel-optimization"></a>

### 创建vercel.json配置文件

在项目根目录创建`vercel.json`文件：

```json
{
  "cleanUrls": true,
  "trailingSlash": false,
  "headers": [
    {
      "source": "/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        {
          "key": "Cache-Control",
          "value": "public, max-age=3600, s-maxage=86400"
        },
        {
          "key": "X-Content-Type-Options",
          "value": "nosniff"
        },
        {
          "key": "X-Frame-Options",
          "value": "DENY"
        },
        {
          "key": "X-XSS-Protection",
          "value": "1; mode=block"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "/assets/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        {
          "key": "Cache-Control",
          "value": "public, max-age=31536000, immutable"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "redirects": [
    {
      "source": "/algorithms",
      "destination": "/",
      "permanent": true
    }
  ]
}
```

### 配置自定义域名

1. 在Vercel仪表板中添加自定义域名`jsdiff.com`
2. 按照Vercel提供的说明配置DNS记录
3. 启用HTTPS

